OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FITV News' Lise McNally reports on Andy
OL,7,FBurnham's first day as prime minister.
OL,9,FAndy Burnham's first day in office has
OL,10,Fseen him vow to end homelessness, meet
OL,11,Fthe King, and invite Donald Trump to
OL,12,FManchester.
OL,14,FBut before addressing the nation or
OL,15,Fintroducing himself to world leaders,
OL,16,Fthe former Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,17,Fbegan his day with a visit to
OL,18,Fhomelessness charity The Passage in
OL,19,FVictoria, London.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
