OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784641699
OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FMr Burnham said his early morning
OL,7,Fvisit was the "best place to start"
OL,8,Fahead of his premiership, visiting
OL,9,Fsuch a charity to see "the lives that
OL,10,Fare being turned around".
OL,12,FSpeaking in Downing Street just a few
OL,13,Fhours later, in his first speech as
OL,14,FPM, he told gathered supporters and
OL,15,Fjournalists: "I will soon go through
OL,16,Fthat door behind me and issue my first
OL,17,Finstruction: to end rough sleeping in
OL,18,Four country."
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@cO]qD@WOUrD@XO]wD@NOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
