OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FLord Hermer, another key ally of the
OL,7,Fformer prime minister, was sacked as
OL,8,Fattorney general, Darren Jones was
OL,9,Fousted as chief secretary to the prime
OL,10,Fminister, Liz Kendall lost her
OL,11,Ftechnology secretary post and Jo
OL,12,FStevens left her Welsh secretary post.
OL,14,FIn his first speech as Prime Minister,
OL,15,FMr Burnham ` whose return to
OL,16,FWestminster triggered Sir Keir's
OL,17,Fresignation ` acknowledged the
OL,18,Fturbulence in British politics which
OL,19,Fmeant he was the seventh prime
OL,20,Fminister since 2016.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
