CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784641699
OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FIt was, he said, a time for
OL,7,F"reflection and new resolution" and
OL,8,F"Britain needs to show the world that
OL,9,Fwe can regain our stability once
OL,10,Fagain".
OL,12,FThe Makerfield MP acknowledged a
OL,13,Fdisaffection among Britons with
OL,14,Fpolitics in general.
OL,16,F"I know people at home are fed up with
OL,17,Fpolitics. I hear you and I want to be
OL,18,Fhonest with you ` we have not been
OL,19,Fgood enough, and we need to be better.
OL,20,FWe will be.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@_O]pD@AOUrD@FO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
