PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784641699
OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,F"We will make this moment a circuit
OL,7,Fbreaker for Britain, bringing forward
OL,8,Fthe biggest changes in the last 40
OL,9,Fyears ` a new political model and a
OL,10,Fnew economic model."
OL,12,FHe suggested that would mean putting
OL,13,F"life's essentials back under stronger
OL,14,Fpublic control to make them
OL,15,Faffordable" and using public spending
OL,16,Fto back British businesses.
OL,18,FMr Burnham said he would set out a 10-
OL,19,Fyear plan later this year but promised
OL,20,Fmore immediate help to deal with
OL,21,Fsqueezed household finances.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]uD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784641699
OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,F"I can do something to give people
OL,7,Fsome breathing space now, some help
OL,8,Fwith the cost of living, and I will
OL,9,Fset out some of those measures
OL,10,Fstarting tomorrow, including how we
OL,11,Fpay for them," he said.
OL,13,FMr Burnham later told reporters he was
OL,14,Flooking at measures including rent
OL,15,Ffreezes, caps on bus fares and help
OL,16,Fwith energy bills although no final
OL,17,Fdecisions have been made.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
