FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784641699
OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FMr Burnham's ability to move is
OL,7,Fconstrained by his commitment to
OL,8,Ffollow the rules on spending and
OL,9,Fborrowing set out by Ms Reeves while
OL,10,Fshe was chancellor and his promise to
OL,11,Fstick to Labour's manifesto commitment
OL,12,Fnot to hike personal taxes for workers.
OL,14,FHe told reporters he would use "any
OL,15,Fflexibility" he could find within the
OL,16,Fexisting rules but "none of this is
OL,17,Fabout taking risks with the economy".
OL,26,@vD@`OUwD@LO]xD@TOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
