OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FMr Burnham said his approach was about
OL,7,Fputting the "right values and the
OL,8,Fright standards" at the heart of
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,F"I will put the care of people at the
OL,12,Fheart of everything I do", he said,
OL,13,Furging Britons to "pull with me" to
OL,14,F"build a new national sense of unity".
OL,26,@oD@MOUpD@PO]sD@AOUtD@YO]uD@SOUuD@`O]vD@
OL,26,AAOUvD@eO]
