OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FMr Burnham's first call as Prime
OL,7,FMinister was with Donald Trump and
OL,8,FDowning Street said he told the US
OL,9,Fpresident he hoped to show him "what
OL,10,FManchester had to offer during a visit
OL,11,Fin the future" amid speculation next
OL,12,Fyear's G20 summit could be held in the
OL,13,FNorth West.
OL,15,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch sent a
OL,16,Fletter welcoming the Prime Minister
OL,17,Fand urging him to commit to spending
OL,18,Fcuts and rule out tax rises.
OL,26,@qD@`OUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
