OL,3,CTrump, rough sleeping, and the King:
OL,4,CAndy Burnham's first day in office
OL,6,FShe also urged him to grant licences
OL,7,Ffor the North Sea's Rosebank and
OL,8,FJackdaw and overturn the ban on new
OL,9,Foil and gas licences.
OL,11,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski
OL,12,Fcalled on Mr Burnham to impose rent
OL,13,Fcontrols, take the water industry into
OL,14,Fpublic ownership and introduce wealth
OL,15,Ftaxes.
OL,17,FMr Burnham swept into Downing Street
OL,18,Fafter being asked to form a government
OL,19,Fby the King following Sir Keir's
OL,20,Fresignation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
